snippet.textDisplay: I love this song, but somewhere I feel like they didn’t do justice to the folk version. I believe that if you’re going for this kind of fusion, our country’s folk artists should get more screen time with proper arrangements. That said, the female singer has absolutely nailed it and brought the song to life!
